DataSource.RecordSource:
SELECT so.Code as SO_No, so.TransDate as SO_TransDate, so.CustomerPurchaseOrderNo, so.SpecialTaxRate as SO_SpecialTaxRate, so.ExportTaxRate as SO_ExportTaxRate, so.SpecialTax as SO_SpecialTax, so.ExportTax as SO_ExportTax, so.VATRate as SO_VATRate, so.VAT as SO_VAT, so.TotalVATAmount as SO_TotalVATAmount, so.TotalExportAmount as SO_TotalExportAmount, so.TotalAmount AS SO_TotalAmount, so.TotalSpecialTaxAmount as SO_TotalSpecialTaxAmount, so.TotalDiscountAmount as SO_TotalDiscountAmount, so.TotalNetAmount as SO_TotalNetAmount,
presentative.Name as Presentative_Name,
shipto.Description + ' (' + shipto.Code + ')' as ShipTo_NameCode, shipto.Address as ShipTo_Address, customer.Name + ' (' + customer.Code + ')' AS Customer_NameCode, customer.Address AS Customer_Address, billto.Description + ' (' + billto.Code + ')' AS BillTo_NameCode, billto.Address AS BillTo_Address, paymentterm.Code AS PaymentTerm_Code, paymentterm.Description AS PaymentTerm_Description, saletype.Code AS SaleType_Code, saletype.Description AS SaleType_Description, product.Code AS Product_Code, product.Revision as Product_Revision, product.Description AS Product_Description, um.Code AS UM_Code, soi.SaleOrderLine as SOI_Line, soi.OrderQuantity as SOI_OrderQuantity, soi.UnitPrice as SOI_UnitPrice, soi.VATAmount as SOI_VATAmount, soi.ExportTaxAmount as SOI_ExportTaxAmount, soi.SpecialTaxAmount as SOI_SpecialTaxAmount, soi.TotalAmount as SOI_TotalAmount, soi.DiscountAmount as SOI_DiscountAmount, soi.ItemCustomerCode as SOI_ItemCustomerCode, soi.ItemCustomerRevision as SOI_ItemCustomerRevision, partycontact.Name as PartyContact_Name, partycontact.Title as PartyContact_Title, partycontact.Phone as PartyContact_Phone, ccn.Name AS CCN_Name, ccn.Phone AS CCN_Phone, ccn.Fax as CCN_Fax, ccn.State as CCN_State
FROM SO_SaleOrderMaster so INNER JOIN SO_SaleOrderDetail soi ON so.SaleOrderMasterID = soi.SaleOrderMasterID INNER JOIN MST_CCN ccn ON so.CCNID = ccn.CCNID LEFT JOIN MST_PartyLocation billto ON so.BillToLocID = billto.PartyLocationID LEFT JOIN MST_PartyLocation shipto ON so.ShipToLocID = shipto.PartyLocationID LEFT JOIN MST_Party customer ON so.PartyID = customer.PartyID LEFT JOIN MST_PaymentTerm paymentterm ON so.PaymentTermsID = paymentterm.PaymentTermID LEFT JOIN MST_Employee presentative ON so.SalesRepresentativeID = presentative.EmployeeID LEFT JOIN SO_SaleType saletype ON so.SaleTypeID = saletype.SaleTypeID LEFT JOIN ITM_Product product ON soi.ProductID = product.ProductID LEFT JOIN MST_UnitOfMeasure um ON soi.SellingUMID = um.UnitOfMeasureID LEFT JOIN MST_PartyContact partycontact ON so.PartyContactID = partycontact.PartyContactID
